<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='5424:5468'>告名<span class='krp-note'>子孫/名也</span>春寒<span class='krp-note'>寒暄/隨時</span>想汝與諸㓜<span class='krp-note'>卑㓜/隨事</span>吉健<span class='krp-note'>述先時/往來書</span>吾</span><br/>
